🧮 Calculator

📌 Overview

This is a simple Calculator Application that performs basic arithmetic operations such as:

Addition (+)

Subtraction (−)

Multiplication (×)

Division (÷)


You can run this calculator simply in vs studio or any c compiler website.



💻 Usage Example

Enter first number: 10  
Enter operation (+, -, *, /): *  
Enter second number: 5  
Result = 50



📂 Project Structure

calculator/
│── calculator.c


💻 Tecnology used

